==English==

===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm|en}} {{term|abaishment|lang=enm}}, from {{etyl|frm|en}} {{term|abaissement||astonishment|lang=frm}} alteration of {{term|esbaissement|lang=frm}}, from {{term|esbaiss|lang=frm}} + {{term|-ment|lang=frm}}.<ref>{{R:MW3 1976|page=2}}</ref>
* Compare French ''[[ébahissement]]''

===Pronunciation===
* {{a|RP}} {{IPA|/əˈbæʃ.mənt/|lang=en}}
* {{a|GenAm}} {{IPA|/əˈbæʃ.mənt/|lang=en}}

